    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《魔法连消与战术大师》是一款结合三消玩法的回合制策略游戏。掌控您的魔法，释放强大的法术，面对各种强敌，拯救被致命魔法瘟疫侵袭的土地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在彩虹学院...学习一门技艺，掌握魔法，并探索您的真正使命。或许，还能拯救世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入新一代年轻巫师的行列，清除有害的环境，战胜敌人，并恢复因两位世仇女巫姐妹之间爆发的远古魔法对决所导致的土地腐蚀的平衡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏特色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189890/extras/489bb6595ee87e8403784961a596d96f.avif?t=1749340310\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您的三消连击决定了移动范围，而三消得分则影响您能造成的伤害。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189890/extras/e1d3fc3233fc04ab28589a5341e0d939.poster.avif?t=1749340310\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189890/extras/e1d3fc3233fc04ab28589a5341e0d939.webm?t=1749340310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189890/extras/e1d3fc3233fc04ab28589a5341e0d939.mp4?t=1749340310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189890/extras/ef0e16ecdbdeb7705ec56fa1c275d099.avif?t=1749340310\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次的游戏都是独一无二的体验，每次都会有不同的房间、敌人和布局，带来全新的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189890/extras/ad0b33cfc23fc9d4bbbf98f4d8e466e1.avif?t=1749340310\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每次游戏过程中，通过收集各种物品创建全新的角色养成。而这些物品将显著改变角色的成长路线和游戏风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189890/extras/afc355bd1af4c9a17af6444a83ef2726.poster.avif?t=1749340310\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189890/extras/afc355bd1af4c9a17af6444a83ef2726.webm?t=1749340310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189890/extras/afc355bd1af4c9a17af6444a83ef2726.mp4?t=1749340310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
